collectors.title: Database
collectors.titleDetails: (8 total Queries, 8 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql: SELECT `p`.`product_id`, `p`.`product_name`, SUM(i.current_stock) as current_stock, SUM(i.available_stock) as available_stock, `p`.`unit_price`, SUM(i.current_stock * p.unit_price) as stock_value, `p`.`minimum_stock` FROM `inventory` `i` LEFT JOIN `products` `p` ON `p`.`product_id` = `i`.`product_id` GROUP BY `p`.`product_id` ORDER BY `p`.`product_name` ASC

timelineData.name: Query
